desc: Jcunicorn is a fine jewelry store founded in NYC, We design, make and sell exquisite jewelry with a affordable prices, Explore our latest jewelry collection discover Jcunicorn's necklaces, earrings, rings and bracelets as well as women's headbands for every look.

layout.text: Dress up your ears and liven up any combination with a pair of earrings from JCunicorn. Whether you prefer a subtle pair of studs, classic drop earrings, a fun pair of hoops, or bold huggie earrings, we have the perfect set for you.
